	(lib_symbols)
	(text "DIGITAL  +  AES OUTPUT
Components:
 - U: PCM4202 ADC (SSOP-28), I2S MASTER, hardware-strapped (M/S,FMT,rate)
 - U: DIT4192 AES Tx (SSOP-28), I2S SLAVE, single-wire   [D9]
 - T: AES Tx transformer (PE-65612NL / SC937-02)   [D4]
 - J: Neutrik NC3MAH male XLR (AES out, 110ohm)
Internal I2S: ADC -> BCK/LRCK/SDATA -> DIT.  MCLK from Clocking.
Control: DIT_SCK/MOSI/CS from MCU.  CONV_RST_N gates ADC+DIT.
AIN*_x from Analog Input sheet."
